pyproject.toml 和 setup.py 是一样的效果

shiv -c async_get_change_data -o mysql_cdc.pyz .
uv pip sync pyproject.toml 会删除已安装未在项目中引用的第三方包
打包pyz的pyproject.toml项目配置文件如下

pyproject.toml
[project]
name = "mysql-cdc"
version = "0.1.0"
description = "Add your description here"
readme = "README.md"
requires-python = ">=3.13"
dependencies = [
    "mysql-replication>=1.0.9",
]

[[tool.uv.index]]
url = "https://pypi.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/simple"
default = true

[tool.setuptools.packages.find]
where = ["."]
#include = ["async_get_change_data*"]  # 指定需要包含的模块
# shiv --site-packages ./.venv/Lib/site-packages -c async_get_change_data -o mysql_cdc.pyz . 指定包的搜索路径

[project.scripts]
async_get_change_data = "async_get_change_data:main"
